Yaupon Garden Club’s annual plant sale set for April 4 It’s time once again for Yaupon Garden Club’s annual plant sale from 9 a.m. to 2 p.m. April 4.

event.title: This year the plant sale will be held

data.event: This year the plant sale will be held from 9 a.m. to 2 p.m. at the Texas Forestry Service located on U.S. 287 /Texas 19, past the Palestine Civic Center, behind Fire Station No. 4.
